{"tid":1566790,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［士氣係用嚟做實事］呢幾日有唱過歌嘅915一定要出嚟遊行","createTime":"2019-09-13T17:59:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T15:56:46.000Z","uid":173326,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"93f4349ecab43a493865e2d2e96f903dc741156b","tid":1566790,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T17:59:11.000Z","msg":"被捕、失去性命嘅人冇辦法過一個正常嘅中秋，香港人呢3個月亦未有過一個正常週末，但暴政仲係寸步不讓。<br />\n<br />\n雖然民調話少數人已經收貨，但我地一定要大聲俾國際知道香港人未收貨，亦唔會讓步妥協、唔會接受階段性成果。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">無論你係溫和定激進，915一定要出嚟大遊行，唔係匿入商場。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">915人數絕對唔可以少過616、818，否則死去嘅朋友會對我地好失望。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地要用人數話俾國際聽：<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>香港人唔會妥協屈服，五大命令缺一不可！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RjomQhk.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRjomQhk.gif&h=33cfdcb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OjtpsoQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOjtpsoQ.gif&h=c1aba121&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=gMYNfQlf1H8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgMYNfQlf1H8&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88iEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=ac0f5e90\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=gMYNfQlf1H8</a><br />\nDo you join the people's side<br />\nUsing the rights of citizens<br />\nIt is the parade of the people<br />\nwho will not be slaves again<br />\nWhen they're bleeding for us all<br />\nFighting for freedom of Hong Kong<br />\nThere is a light of mankind<br />\nwhen more people come～"},{"pid":"89f88b51e1caf2ac0052eefbc755826bf64ef2c6","tid":1566790,"uid":234159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T17:59:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><s